{"tid":2029793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這是一場持久戰啊屌你","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T13:04:37.000Z","uid":150907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3badedfbf0063ed22fc305f892c35ed1855b7a04","tid":2029793,"uid":150907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"各位<br />\n這是持久戰的<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得一路走來<br />\n都有好多話終極一戰的日子<br />\n<br />\n意指想我們如果當日打不過他的話<br />\n我們就自己收皮<br />\n<br />\n反其道而行<br />\n我們不當是終極一戰<br />\n<br />\n以游刃有餘般長期作戰<br />\n這才對得住永遠留在2019年的朋友<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n請記住<br />\n這是持久戰<br />\n<br />\n我們停止之日<br />\n將是香港光復之時<br />\n<br />\n共勉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />攬炒吧股市、樓市同藍絲"},{"pid":"d64e66a468eefad7c182df23bb14236d1c8ede38","tid":2029793,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"524 維園見"},{"pid":"727e4b111ff7ec0afd2411879b031cc2979e2f60","tid":2029793,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:59:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vugdAiZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvugdAiZ.gif&h=7083d6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z86kZLF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz86kZLF.jpg&h=c11f4c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7QMX1Y0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7QMX1Y0.jpg&h=ff057371&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔出嘅話</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MyDSQSo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMyDSQSo.gif&h=31b5d12e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42c114c087daefdb206318e6a08c2ccc0a772b1f","tid":2029793,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"唯一長久既辦法就只有香港獨立<br />\n真係冇得揀"},{"pid":"35e2dd2add00c658d4771c39158b6cc58ba7fa14","tid":2029793,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"攬炒同流浮山刀手唔知邊個到先"},{"pid":"19687577aa9d137954bef0bfcef2a54713ebfdea","tid":2029793,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:04:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"}]}